Quadratic Equation  

<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[117, 225, 381, 242]]<|/det|>
For the equation \(ax^{2} + bx + c = 0\)  

<|ref|>equation<|/ref|><|det|>[[421, 242, 572, 281]]<|/det|>
\[x = \frac{-b\pm\sqrt{b^{2} - 4ac}}{2a}\]  

<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[80, 313, 227, 328]]<|/det|>
Binomial Theorem  

<|ref|>equation<|/ref|><|det|>[[242, 334, 751, 371]]<|/det|>
\[(a + b)^{n} = a^{n} + \binom{n}{1} a^{n - 1}b + \binom{n}{2} a^{n - 2}b^{2} + \ldots +\binom{n}{r} a^{n - r}b^{r} + \ldots +b^{n},\]  

<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[117, 380, 493, 415]]<|/det|>
where \(n\) is a positive integer and \(\binom{n}{r} = \frac{n!}{(n - r)!r!}\)

<|ref|>equation<|/ref|><|det|>[[404, 662, 590, 696]]<|/det|>

<|ref|>equation<|/ref|><|det|>[[402, 716, 593, 770]]<|/det|>

Mathematical Formulae  

<|ref|>sub_title<|/ref|><|det|>[[436, 138, 552, 154]]<|/det|>
## 1. ALGEBRA  

<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[88, 170, 240, 185]]<|/det|>
Quadratic Equation  

<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[115, 199, 368, 215]]<|/det|>
For the equation \(ax^{2} + bx + c = 0\)  

<|ref|>equation<|/ref|><|det|>[[413, 216, 575, 252]]<|/det|>
\[x = \frac{-b\pm\sqrt{b^{2} - 4ac}}{2a}\]  

<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[88, 268, 229, 282]]<|/det|>
Binomial Theorem  

<|ref|>equation<|/ref|><|det|>[[251, 286, 736, 325]]<|/det|>
\[(a + b)^{n} = a^{n} + \binom{n}{1} a^{n - 1}b + \binom{n}{2} a^{n - 2}b^{2} + \ldots +\binom{n}{r} a^{n - r}b^{r} + \ldots +b^{n}\]  

<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[115, 333, 477, 370]]<|/det|>
where \(n\) is a positive integer and \(\binom{n}{r} = \frac{n!}{(n - r)!r!}\)  

<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[88, 394, 385, 410]]<|/det|>
Arithmetic series \(u_{n} = a + (n - 1)d\)  

<|ref|>equation<|/ref|><|det|>[[255, 415, 521, 440]]<|/det|>
\[S_{n} = \frac{1}{2} n(a + l) = \frac{1}{2} n\{2a + (n - 1)d\}\]  

<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[88, 467, 216, 481]]<|/det|>
Geometric series  

<|ref|>equation<|/ref|><|det|>[[255, 465, 415, 555]]<|/det|>
\[u_{n} = a r^{n - 1}\] \[S_{n} = \frac{a(1 - r^{n})}{1 - r} (r\neq 1)\] \[S_{\infty} = \frac{a}{1 - r} (|r|< 1)\]  

<|ref|>sub_title<|/ref|><|det|>[[402, 576, 585, 591]]<|/det|>
## 2. TRIGONOMETRY  

<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[88, 606, 160, 621]]<|/det|>
Identities  

<|ref|>equation<|/ref|><|det|>[[421, 620, 572, 670]]<|/det|>
\[\sin^{2}A + \cos^{2}A = 1\] \[\sec^{2}A = 1 + \tan^{2}A\] \[\csc^{2}A = 1 + \cot^{2}A\]  

<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[88, 700, 243, 714]]<|/det|>
Formulae for \(\Delta ABC\)  

<|ref|>equation<|/ref|><|det|>[[405, 716, 578, 750]]<|/det|>
\[\frac{a}{\sin A} = \frac{b}{\sin B} = \frac{c}{\sin C}\]  

<|ref|>equation<|/ref|><|det|>[[404, 760, 583, 777]]<|/det|>
\[a^{2} = b^{2} + c^{2} - 2bc\cos A\]  

<|ref|>equation<|/ref|><|det|>[[437, 787, 550, 813]]<|/det|>
\[\Delta = \frac{1}{2} bc\sin A\]<｜end▁of▁sentence｜>

## 1. ALGEBRA  

<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[79, 165, 238, 181]]<|/det|>
Quadratic Equation  

<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[116, 194, 384, 212]]<|/det|>
For the equation \(ax^{2} + bx + c = 0\) ,  

<|ref|>equation<|/ref|><|det|>[[415, 211, 580, 247]]<|/det|>
\[x = \frac{-b\pm\sqrt{b^{2} - 4ac}}{2a}\]  

<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[79, 271, 226, 286]]<|/det|>
Binomial Theorem  

<|ref|>equation<|/ref|><|det|>[[244, 290, 750, 329]]<|/det|>
\[(a + b)^{n} = a^{n} + \binom{n}{1} a^{n - 1}b + \binom{n}{2} a^{n - 2}b^{2} + \ldots +\binom{n}{r} a^{n - r}b^{r} + \ldots +b^{n}\]  

<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[116, 345, 496, 379]]<|/det|>
where \(n\) is a positive integer and \(\binom{n}{r} = \frac{n!}{(n - r)!r!}\)  

<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[79, 410, 384, 426]]<|/det|>
Arithmetic series \(u_{n} = a + (n - 1)d\)  

<|ref|>equation<|/ref|><|det|>[[245, 432, 532, 463]]<|/det|>
\[S_{n} = \frac{1}{2} n(a + l) = \frac{1}{2} n\{2a + (n - 1)d\}\]  

<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[79, 487, 333, 503]]<|/det|>
Geometric series \(u_{n} = ar^{n - 1}\)  

<|ref|>equation<|/ref|><|det|>[[245, 508, 428, 576]]<|/det|>
\[S_{n} = \frac{a(1 - r^{n})}{1 - r} (r\neq 1)\] \[S_{\infty} = \frac{a}{1 - r} (|r|< 1)\]  

<|ref|>sub_title<|/ref|><|det|>[[401, 610, 593, 626]]<|/det|>
## 2. TRIGONOMETRY  

<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[79, 642, 155, 657]]<|/det|>
Identities  

<|ref|>equation<|/ref|><|det|>[[415, 670, 581, 720]]<|/det|>
\[\sin^{2}A + \cos^{2}A = 1\] \[\sec^{2}A = 1 + \tan^{2}A\] \[\csc \sec^{2}A = 1 + \cot^{2}A\]  

<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[79, 765, 240, 780]]<|/det|>
Formulae for \(\Delta ABC\)  

<|ref|>equation<|/ref|><|det|>[[404, 790, 593, 880]]<|/det|>
\[\frac{a}{\sin A} = \frac{b}{\sin B} = \frac{c}{\sin C\] \[a^{2} = b^{2} + c^{2} - 2bc\cos A\] \[\Delta = \frac{1}{2} bc\sin A\]<｜end▁of▁sentence｜>

where \(n\) is a positive integer and \(\binom{n}{r} = \frac{n!}{(n - r)!r!}\)  

<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[88, 393, 385, 409]]<|/det|>

<|ref|>equation<|/ref|><|det|>[[254, 412, 521, 440]]<|/det|>
\[S_{n} = \frac{1}{2} n(a + l) = \frac{1}{2} n\{2a + (n - 1)d\}\]  

<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[88, 466, 220, 481]]<|/det|>

<|ref|>equation<|/ref|><|det|>[[254, 465, 415, 555]]<|/det|>

<|ref|>equation<|/ref|><|det|>[[417, 215, 585, 250]]<|/det|>

<|ref|>equation<|/ref|><|det|>[[246, 294, 753, 330]]<|/det|>
\[(a+b)^n = a^n + \binom{n}{1}a^{n-1}b + \binom{n}{2}a^{n-2}b^2 + \ldots + \binom{n}{r}a^{n-r}b^r + \ldots + b^n\]

<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[119, 348, 499, 382]]<|/det|>
where \(n\) is a positive integer and \(\binom{n}{r} = \frac{n!}{(n-r)!r!}\)

Arithmetic series 

<|ref|>equation<|/ref|><|det|>[[248, 412, 390, 430]]<|/det|>

# 1. ALGEBRA 

<|ref|>sub_title<|/ref|><|det|>[[80, 166, 243, 183]]<|/det|>
## Quadratic Equation 

<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[118, 195, 388, 214]]<|/det|>
For the equation \(ax^2 + bx + c = 0\), 

<|ref|>equation<|/ref|><|det|>[[415, 213, 585, 249]]<|/det|>
\[x = \frac{-b \pm \sqrt{b^2 - 4ac}}{2a}\]

<|ref|>sub_title<|/ref|><|det|>[[80, 272, 230, 288]]<|/det|>
## Binomial Theorem 

<|ref|>equation<|/ref|><|det|>[[245, 290, 752, 329]]<|/det|>
\[(a+b)^n = a^n + \binom{n}{1}a^{n-1}b + \binom{n}{2}a^{n-2}b^2 + \dots + \binom{n}{r}a^{n-r}b^r + \dots + b^n\]

<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[118, 345, 500, 381]]<|/det|>
where \(n\) is a positive integer and \(\binom{n}{r} = \frac{n!}{(n-r)!r!}\) 

<|ref|>sub_title<|/ref|><|det|>[[80, 411, 375, 428]]<|/det|>
## Arithmetic series \(u_n = a + (n-1)d\) 

<|ref|>equation<|/ref|><|det|>[[245, 433, 536, 464]]<|/det|>
\[S_n = \frac{1}{2}n(a+l) = \frac{1}{2}n\{2a+(n-1)d\}\]

<|ref|>sub_title<|/ref|><|det|>[[80, 488, 336, 505]]<|/det|>
## Geometric series \(u_n = ar^{n-1}\) 

<|ref|>equation<|/ref|><|det|>[[245, 508, 430, 580]]<|/det|>
\[S_n = \frac{a(1-r^n)}{1-r} \quad (r \neq 1) \\ S_\infty = \frac{a}{1-r} \quad (|r| < 1)\]

<|ref|>sub_title<|/ref|><|det|>[[400, 612, 595, 629]]<|/det|>

<|ref|>sub_title<|/ref|><|det|>[[80, 768, 245, 784]]<|/det|>
## Formulae for \(\Delta ABC\) 

<|ref|>equation<|/ref|><|det|>[[404, 793, 595, 830]]<|/det|>
\[\frac{a}{\sin A} = \frac{b}{\sin B} = \frac{c}{\sin C}\]

<|ref|>equation<|/ref|><|det|>[[404, 827, 595, 848]]<|/det|>

<|ref|>equation<|/ref|><|det|>[[440, 853, 556, 882]]<|/det|>

Binomial Theorem  

<|ref|>equation<|/ref|><|det|>[[259, 297, 765, 336]]<|/det|>
\[(a + b)^{n} = a^{n} + \binom{n}{1} a^{n - 1}b + \binom{n}{2} a^{n - 2}b^{2} + \ldots +\binom{n}{r} a^{n - r}b^{r} + \ldots +b^{n}\]  

<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[132, 351, 512, 390]]<|/det|>
where \(n\) is a positive integer and \(\binom{n}{r} = \frac{n!}{(n - r)!r!}\)

<|ref|>equation<|/ref|><|det|>[[260, 441, 549, 470]]<|/det|>

<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[95, 494, 350, 510]]<|/det|>

<|ref|>equation<|/ref|><|det|>[[260, 515, 444, 580]]<|/det|>

<|ref|>equation<|/ref|><|det|>[[234, 336, 760, 375]]<|/det|>
\[(a + b)^{n} = a^{n} + \binom{n}{1} a^{n - 1}b + \binom{n}{2} a^{n - 2}b^{2} + \ldots +\binom{n}{r} a^{n - r}b^{r} + \ldots +b^{n},\]  

<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[118, 384, 503, 420]]<|/det|>
where \(n\) is a positive integer and \(\binom{n}{r} = \frac{n!}{(n - r)!r!}\)

\[\sin^{2}A + \cos^{2}A = 1\] \[\sec^{2}A = 1 + \tan^{2}A\] \[\csc^{2}A = 1 + \cot^{2}A\]

Formulae for \(\Delta ABC\)  

<|ref|>equation<|/ref|><|det|>[[400, 666, 595, 700]]<|/det|>
\[\frac{a}{\sin A} = \frac{b}{\sin B} = \frac{c}{\sin C}\]  

<|ref|>equation<|/ref|><|det|>[[400, 720, 595, 738]]<|/det|>
\[a^{2} = b^{2} + c^{2} - 2bc\cos A\]  

<|ref|>equation<|/ref|><|det|>[[437, 746, 558, 775]]<|/det|>
\[\Delta = \frac{1}{2} bc\sin A\]<｜end▁of▁sentence｜>
